></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #ffcc00;\">Builders has always embraced our clients and partners as part of Our Team.  Every project is performed with open communication.  The Partnering methodology is implemented and a mutual respect with our clients provides the groundwork for our success.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffcc00;\">Our Mission:</span></h1>\r\n<p class=\"LC20lb\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #ffcc00;\">The mission of Builders is to provide an outstanding level of service and expertise in the real estate market that is innovative and ambitious. Builders is dedicated to the highest standards, systems and performance necessary to fulfill all of your real estate dreams.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"LC20lb\"> </p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class=\"LC20lb\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\">Our Vision:</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"LC20lb\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #ffcc00;\">The satisfaction of our customers is the main priority of Builders. Our goal is to be a point of reference in everything related to Real Estate   To make the Real Estate buying and selling of real estate as cost effective as possible while maintaining the highest level of service. Along with providing accurate and up-to-date information, skilled analysis and sound real estate advice and to continually explore new ideas and technology, to make the selling and buying of real estate faster, less costly, and easier.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"LC20lb\"> </p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\">Our Values:</span></strong></span></h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 12pt;\">Integrity</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 12pt;\">Honesty</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 12pt;\">Respect</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 12pt;\">Professionalism</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 12pt;\">Unquestionable Ethics</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 12pt;\">Commitment</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 12pt;\">Teamwork</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 12pt;\">Social Responsibility</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 12pt;\">Customer Service Excellence</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Q9OW58VJf5s\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe> </span></p>','',1,2,'2019-01-29 07:02:11',42,'','2019-03-17 09:14:31',42,42,'2019-03-17 09:14:31','2019-01-29 07:02:11','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"images\\/joomlart\\/features\\/item-14.jpg\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',34,4,'','',1,362,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'en-GB','',''),(26,124,'Decoration & Finishing Services','decorations','<p>Our interior design and decoration services are a complete overall handling of interior and exterior aspects of our projects. Our main goal is to synchronize all project’s surfaces starting from the outside facade all through the final finishes of the interior walls and decoration. </p>\r\n<p> This exclusive service includes wall painting and wallpapers, tiling, roof, Lightings , gypsum and general color coordination matching the exterior features of the project in addition to landscape and exterior gardens surrounding the premises. </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #ffcc00;\">Advantages of Gypsum Board walls and ceilings:</span></h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\r\n<p>Gypsum board is often called drywall, wallboard, or plasterboard. It differs from other panel-type building products, because of its noncombustible core and paper facers. When joints and fastener heads are covered with a joint compound system, gypsum wall board creates a continuous surface suitable for most types of interior decoration. </p>\r\n<p> Ease of installation</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fire resistance</li>\r\n<li>Sound isolation</li>\r\n<li>Durability</li>\r\n<li>Economy</li>\r\n<li>Versatility</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"post-title\"> </h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"post-title\"><span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\">Ceramic Walls and Flooring:</span></h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\r\n<div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">Ceramic is a very versatile material. Cast your eyes over the selection of ceramic tiles below, and we’re sure you’ll agree with us. We’ve used it to create everything from sleek, contemporary brick-shaped tiles, through to realistic wood effect floor tiles. Come and find a stylish new addition for your bedroom, bathroom, kitchen or living room.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\r\n<div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\r\n<h3 class=\"post-title\"> </h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"post-title\"><span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\">Granite and Marble:</span></h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\r\n<div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\r\n<p>Natural Stone Steps and Staircases are a distinctive feature of many of the finest properties.  Builders have fitted stone steps and marble staircases in all our properties in Egypt over the years.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We make the best entrances:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Stone selection advice in relation to design and application.</li>\r\n<li>Sourcing of a wide variety of stone</li>\r\n<li>Production of the steps or staircase by our skilled stone masons for high quality finishes.</li>\r\n<li>Installation of the steps or staircase by our experienced and highly skilled teams of fitting stone masons.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"post-title\"> </h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"post-title\"><span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\">UPVC Windows:</span></h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\r\n<div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\r\n<p>UPVC windows are built to last. They are manufactured to the highest quality and they won’t rot, rust, peel or flake – all they need is an occasional wipe down with soapy water to keep them looking their best.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Low maintenance</strong> – White or coloured uPVC window frames don’t need painting or sealing, significantly reducing maintenance over their life time. They are easily cleaned with water and detergent.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Tough and durable</strong> – uPVC is a very durable material used in water and sewer pipes for at least 100 years.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Rot resistant</strong> – uPVC does not rot, and is resistant to corrosion.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Thermal comfort</strong> – Unlike metals, uPVC is non-conductive, meaning its use in window frames does not transfer heat and therefore contributes to a more consistent internal temperature in a building. The combination of uPVC frames and double glazing makes for highly energy efficient windows.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Openable Tilt and Turn – </strong>uPVC window systems allow opening in two directions to enhance the ability of taking advantage of natural, cross ventilation.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Acoustic insulation</strong>  – Double-glazed uPVC windows and doors are able to cut down noise by as much as 70%.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Resistant to salt erosion</strong> – uPVC is resistant to corrosion caused by salt-laden air making them ideal for coastal properties.</li>\r\n<li><strong>High security</strong> – uPVC windows incorporate multi locking systems providing a high level of security for homes or businesses.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">   </p>\r\n</div>','',1,2,'2019-02-02 20:42:15',42,'','2019-03-05 09:31:40',42,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2019-02-02 20:42:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"