 with a direct view of the sea and pool view<\\/span><br \\/><br \\/><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffcc00;\\\">Apartment is fully furnished new brands and equipped. Ready to stay<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffcc00;\\\">Samra Bay Hotel and Resort is set in Hurghada, 11 km from New Marina, and features a private beach area, 4 outdoor swimming pools and a fitness centre. Featuring a garden, the 5-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms. The accommodation provides a 24-hour front desk and an ATM for guests.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffcc00;\\\">Guest rooms at the hotel are fitted with a seating area. The rooms include a private bathroom, while some boast a sea view. At Samra Bay Hotel and Resort every room has a flat-screen TV with cable channels.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffcc00;\\\">A buffet breakfast, lunch and dinner are served daily at the property.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffcc00;\\\">You can play table tennis at this 5-star hotel, and limousine service is available.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffcc00;\\\">The nearest airport is Hurghada International Airport, 8 km from the hotel.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><iframe style=\\\"border: 0;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.google.com\\/maps\\/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3036.9178631342406!2d33.82485241452594!3d27.156147156106346!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x145280e9b37cab73%3A0x711d2543c39d0ed5!2sSamra+Bay+Hotel+and+Resort!5e1!3m2!1sen!2seg!4v1550434884768\\\" width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"450\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"allowfullscreen\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br \\/><br \\/><br \\/><br \\/><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"12\",\"created\":\"2019-01-29 07:02:11\",\"created_by\":\"42\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-02-1