:\\\"\\\",\\\"project-type\\\":\\\"Luxurious apartment\\\",\\\"location\\\":\\\"Hurghada - Egypt\\\",\\\"other-info\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":17,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"9\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}',0),(211,17,1,'','2019-02-17 21:20:59',42,7481,'e5a6787f817ba16a9abea4c372298d10794414f3','{\"id\":17,\"asset_id\":\"98\",\"title\":\"El Andalous, Sahl Hasheesh, Egypt\",\"alias\":\"el-andalous-sahl-hasheesh\",\"introtext\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">AN AMAZING APARTMENT FOR SALE!<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Sahl Hasheesh private resort<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Red Sea<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Egypt<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">A stunning (110m) 2 bedroom\\/2 bathroom apartment with sea views, just next to the beach. It is being sold fully luxury furnished.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Reduced price: 110,000 GBP<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/42969353_1996527743720039_1480769264687251456_n.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">El Andalous is a luxury apart-hotel right by the beautiful beach at Sahl Hasheesh. It has an attractive Egyptian style reception area which is manned 24\\/7, which leads to the well kept gardens with two beautiful swimming pools and a waterfall. The pool area has sunbeds and sun umbrellas which are free to use. As you walk through the gardens you have excellent views over the pier and beach. There is also a private beach, by the apartments and the pier, with sun-loungers and parasols. Steps lead down to the private beach, promenade and a small shop for your everyday needs.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">There is also an exclusive, private roof pool for the use of apartment owners only.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">\\u00a0El Andalous, is a two bedroom \\/ two bathroom apartment, which sleeps four people (plus a cot for a baby is provided, if required). It is air-conditioned throughout and has been beautifully equipped with quality furniture. All the fixtures and fittings are of a high standard. It has a good sized balcony area with seating, offering views over the beach, pier, pretty gardens and pool.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Lounge &amp; Dining Area: The open plan lounge \\/ diner \\/ kitchen is a good sized area, with a high quality solid kitchen and an attractive dining table and chairs. The lounge has a comfortable sofa and two chairs, satellite TV, coffee tables, with patio doors opening onto the balcony and views of the Red Sea, Sunken City, pier, garden and pools.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Bedrooms: There is an attractive master bedroom, with double bed, a good sized wardrobe, chest of drawers, bedside cabinets, air-conditioning and a patio door leading to a second balcony. It has a large en-suite shower room. The twin bedroom has two single beds, wardrobe, chest of drawers, a bedside table, travel cot, window seat and air-conditioning, with a view of the beach, pool and garden.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Bathrooms: There are two bathrooms which are attractively tiled, with modern sink unit and WC, space age shower cubicles, with lights and steam room setting. Towels are supplied (including beach towels).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Kitchen: Is fully equipped with all you will require. It has an oven, touch-control electric hob, microwave, fridge-freezer, kettle and washing machine.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Balconies &amp; Outside Space: The main balcony, partly enclosed, has a table and chairs, a comfortable bench (with scuba-diving equipment storage) and views to the Red Sea, gardens and pool area. Room for drying clothes (airer supplied) is on the smaller balcony. Patio doors from the main balcony lead to the lounge.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Sahl Hasheesh is a purpose-built paradise on the Red Sea Riviera, It offers up everything from an under-water \'sunken city\' to a fabulous white sand beach which seems to stretch for miles. Surrounded by beautiful bays with stunning beaches leading to the crystal clear blue waters of the Red Sea you can choose to laze on its beaches whilst soaking up the sun, snorkel, scuba dive, visit the local bars, restaurants and shops or relax in the magical Piazza area.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">As you can imagine from such a new resort, everything is incredibly clean and stylish. In particular, there\'s an elegantly designed pier of white stone leading into the Red Sea and a Sunken City has even been created beneath the water as a home for the exotic species of fish found here. You are able to snorkel and scuba-dive around this area. The Piazza in itself is a real marvel, with Egyptian style lamps, fountains and a shimmering man-made canal. At night, it\'s lit up in beautiful colours of neon pink, green and purple.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Sahl Hasheesh International Resort is located approximately 18 km south of Hurghada, and is set to become the largest fully integrated resort area on the Red Sea coast of Egypt. The area enjoys expansive views of the Red Sea, mountains and coast line, clearly exhibiting the beauty of its location, surroundings and natural landscape.<\\/span><br \\/><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Sahl Hasheesh is highly accessible being just 20 minutes drive from Hurghada, itself a prominent holiday destination.<a style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\" href=\\\"index.php?option=com_contact&amp;view=contact&amp;id=1&amp;catid=4\\\">Builders<\\/a><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0<iframe style=\\\"border: 0;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.google.com\\/maps\\/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3553.4484958979187!2d33.89526831452349!3d27.047587760783074!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x144d7dc52f1ffedb%3A0xc4fe2ef1b7954f9d!2sEl+Andalous+Apartments!5e0!3m2!1sen!2seg!4v1550417790554\\\" width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"450\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"allowfullscreen\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\"><img style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"images\\/IMG_3713.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\"><img style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"images\\/IMG_3717.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":\"12\",\"created\":\"2019-01-29 07:02:11\",\"created_by\":\"42\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-02-17 21:20:59\",\"modified_by\":\"42\",\"checked_out\":\"42\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2019-02-17 21:20:52\",\"publish_up\":\"2019-01-29 07:02:11\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/projects\\\\\\/elandalous\\\\\\/card1.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/sahl-hashesh\\\\\\/DSC_3872-3.jpg\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"project-type\\\":\\\"LUXURIOUS APARTMENT\\\",\\\"location\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"other-info\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":31,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"100\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}',0),(212,26,1,'','2019-02-17 21:31:56',42,7676,'37ee50495a42d420b71b26099b0a35771b89b8b6','{\"id\":26,\"asset_id\":\"124\",\"title\":\"Decoration & Finishing Services\",\"alias\":\"decorations\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Our interior design and decoration services are a complete overall handling of interior and exterior aspects of our projects. Our main goal is to synchronize all project\\u2019s surfaces starting from the outside fa\\u00e7ade all through the final finishes of the interior walls and decoration.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0This exclusive service includes wall painting and wallpapers, tiling, roof, lightings, gypsum and general color coordination matching the exterior features of the project in addition to landscape and exterior gardens surrounding the premises.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; color: #ffcc00;\\\">Advantages of Gypsum Board\\u00a0walls and ceilings:<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\\\">\\r\\n<p>Gypsum board is often called drywall, wallboard, or plasterboard. It differs from other panel-type building products, because of its noncombustible core and paper facers. When joints and fastener heads are covered with a joint compound system, gypsum wall board creates a continuous surface suitable for\\u00a0most\\u00a0types of interior decoration.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0Ease of installation<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Fire resistance<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Sound isolation<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Durability<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Economy<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Versatility<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h3 class=\\\"post-title\\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<h3 class=\\\"post-title\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Ceramic Walls and Flooring:<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_wrapper\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_wrapper\\\">Ceramic is a very versatile material. Cast your eyes over the selection of ceramic tiles below, and we\\u2019re sure you\\u2019ll agree with us. We\\u2019ve used it to create everything from sleek, contemporary brick-shaped tiles, through to realistic wood effect floor tiles. Come and find a stylish new addition for your bedroom, bathroom, kitchen or living room.<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_wrapper\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_wrapper\\\">\\r\\n<h3 class=\\\"post-title\\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<h3 class=\\\"post-title\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">Granite and Marble:<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_wrapper\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_wrapper\\\">\\r\\n<p>Natural Stone Steps and Staircases are a distinctive feature of many of the finest properties. \\u00a0Builders have fitted stone steps and marble staircases in all our\\u00a0properties in egypt\\u00a0over the years.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>We make the best entrances:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Stone selection advice in relation to design and application.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Sourcing of a wide variety of stone<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Production of the steps or staircase by our\\u00a0skilled stone masons for high quality finishes.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Installation of the steps or staircase by our experienced and highly skilled teams of fitting stone masons.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h3 class=\\\"post-title\\\">\\u00a0<\\/h3>\\r\\n<h3 class=\\\"post-title\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00;\\\">UPVC Windows:<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_wrapper\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wpb_wrapper\\\">\\r\\n<p>UPVC windows are built to last. They are manufactured to the highest quality and they won\\u2019t rot, rust, peel or flake \\u2013 all they need is an occasional wipe down with soapy water to keep them looking their best.<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><strong>Low maintenance<\\/strong>\\u00a0\\u2013 White or coloured uPVC window frames don\\u2019t need painting or sealing, significantly reducing maintenance over their life time. They are easily cleaned with water and detergent.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Tough and durable<\\/strong>\\u00a0\\u2013 uPVC is a very durable material used in water and sewer pipes for at least 100 years.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Rot resistant<\\/strong>\\u00a0\\u2013 uPVC does not rot, and is resistant to corrosion.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Thermal comfort<\\/strong>\\u00a0\\u2013 Unlike metals, uPVC is non-conductive, meaning its use in window frames does not transfer heat and therefore contributes to a more consistent internal temperature in a building. The combination of uPVC frames and double glazing makes for highly energy efficient windows.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Openable Tilt and Turn \\u2013\\u00a0<\\/strong>uPVC window systems allow opening in two directions to enhance the ability of taking advantage of natural, cross ventilation.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Acoustic insulation<\\/strong>\\u00a0 \\u2013 Double-glazed uPVC windows and doors are able to cut down noise by as much as 70%.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Resistant to salt erosion<\\/strong>\\u00a0\\u2013 uPVC is resistant to corrosion caused by salt-laden air making them ideal for coastal properties.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>High security<\\/strong>\\u00a0\\u2013 uPVC windows incorporate multi locking systems providing a high level of security for homes or businesses.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0<iframe src=\\\"\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/2MK9wM9zlD0\\\" width=\\\"560\\\" height=\\\"314\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"allowfullscreen\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2019-02-02 20:42:15\",\"created_by\":\"42\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-02-17 21:31:56\",\"modified_by\":\"42\",\"checked_out\":\"42\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2019-02-17 21:31:15\",\"publish_up\":\"2019-02-02 20:42:15\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_lay