strong>Walls:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Conrch + 2 paste knives + finishing paint for both the Reception and Rooms<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>Carpentry:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Fully completed from apartment door to the interior doors.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>Windows:<\\/strong>\\u00a0UPVC<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>Electricity:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Fully established<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>Elevators:<\\/strong>\\u00a02 Elevators installed<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"color: #ffcc00; font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>Entrance:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Entrance is made out of marble<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/ALEXANDRIA\\/SPORTING\\/Day-view.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/ALEXANDRIA\\/SPORTING\\/Balacony-view.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/ALEXANDRIA\\/SPORTING\\/GOPR6455.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">{loadmodule id:112}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<iframe style=\\\"border: 0;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.google.com\\/maps\\/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d853.0138095227644!2d29.93333964488475!3d31.21919898752022!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14f5c48c09049395%3A0x6da5831f7a5450e2!2s14+Sidi+Gabir%2C+Qism+Sidi+Gabir%2C+Alexandria+Governorate!5e0!3m2!1sen!2seg!4v1551779545471\\\" width=\\\"600\\\" height=\\\"450\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"allowfullscreen\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"12\",\"created\":\"2019-01-29 07:02:11\",\"created_by\":\"42\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-